thread.title: Justin Brandt

author: Justin Brandt
title: Justin Brandt
text: LaserAway is always a very professional place. I have had 7 sessions on my tattoo now and the results are real! Be warned that it does take time because some people are looking for an overnight result. Not gonna happen. It all depends on your age and color of your tattoo but this place is great. I highly recommend them to anyone looking for a laser treatment for their tattoo or anything else.
